OL,3,CMan who drove at 100mph sentenced for
OL,4,Cdangerous driving and child neglect
OL,6,FA man who drove at 100mph before
OL,7,Fcrashing on the M40, while a child was
OL,8,Fin the car, has been given a suspended
OL,9,Fsentence.
OL,11,FDashcam footage from other motorists
OL,12,Fshows Miley Connors, 37, speeding
OL,13,Falong the motorway in a silver SUV.
OL,15,FOfficers were alerted to Connor's
OL,16,Fdangerous driving at around 4.10pm on
OL,17,F29 December 2021, when they received
OL,18,Fmultiple calls from members of the
OL,19,Fpublic.
