OL,6,FOther drivers reported seeing Connors
OL,7,Ftravelling down the hard shoulder of
OL,8,Fthe southbound carriageway and
OL,9,Fswerving in between traffic. His route
OL,10,Fbegan in Warwickshire and continued
OL,11,Finto Oxfordshire and Buckinghamshire.
OL,13,FConnor's car then hit the central
OL,14,Freservation on the Shabbington bend
OL,15,Fbetween junctions nine and 8A, causing
OL,16,Fit to spin and lose a tyre.
OL,17,FMiraculously no other vehicles were
OL,18,Fhit.
