OL,3,CMan who drove at 100mph sentenced for
OL,4,Cdangerous driving and child neglect
OL,6,FConnors, of Scant Road East, Hambrook,
OL,7,FWest Sussex, carried on driving until
OL,8,Fhe reached an overbridge near
OL,9,FWorminghall, where he got out and
OL,10,Furinated.
OL,12,FA child then fled the car and ran away
OL,13,Fup by the embankment.
OL,15,FOfficers, with help from the National
OL,16,FPolice Air Service, found and arrested
OL,17,FConnors. The child was taken to safety.
OL,19,FConnors was charged the following day.
