OL,3,CMan who drove at 100mph sentenced for
OL,4,Cdangerous driving and child neglect
OL,6,FA jury at Oxford Crown Court
OL,7,Funanimously found Connors guilty of
OL,8,Fdangerous driving and child neglect on
OL,9,F16 February.
OL,11,FHe was sentenced to two years in
OL,12,Fprison, suspended for two years, on
OL,13,FFriday 12 April.
OL,15,FThe judge also disqualified Connors
OL,16,Ffrom driving for two years and he will
OL,17,Fneed to pass an extended retest to get
OL,18,Fhis licence back.
