OL,3,CMan who drove at 100mph sentenced for
OL,4,Cdangerous driving and child neglect
OL,6,FThe judge also ordered Connors to
OL,7,Fcomplete 250 hours of unpaid work, 120
OL,8,Fdays of alcohol monitoring, and an
OL,9,Faccredited thinking skills programme
OL,10,Fwithin 20 days, as well as paying
OL,11,F#3,000 in a fine and costs.
OL,13,FInvestigating officer PC Amy Boughton,
OL,14,FThames Valley Police said: "This was
OL,15,Fone of the worse pieces of driving I
OL,16,Fhave ever seen.
OL,18,F"Not only is it shocking to watch,
OL,19,Fit's gut-wrenching to know there was a
OL,20,Fyoung child in that vehicle, scared
OL,21,Fand crying.
