OL,6,F"The child was found wet, muddy and
OL,7,Fcold, and stood over Miley Connors,
OL,8,Fwho was throwing up and incapable of
OL,9,Flooking after them.
OL,11,F"I can only hope that Connors take
OL,12,Fthis second chance and makes
OL,13,Frecompense for the lives he could have
OL,14,Fso easily taken because of his
OL,15,Freckless actions."
